Description:
    Create or update ManageIQ UI plugin

Example:
    rails generate manageiq:ui_plugin ManageIQ::UiPluginName
    rails generate manageiq:ui_plugin ManageIQ::UiPluginName --path ~/dev
    rails generate manageiq:ui_plugin ManageIQ::UiPluginName --vcr --dummy
    rails generate manageiq:ui_plugin ManageIQ::UiPluginName --vcr --dummy --dev
